@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Helvetica"
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

left to right direction

actor "Customer" as Customer
actor "Store Owner" as Owner

package "Store Edge (Browser)" #f0fdf4 {
  component "Self-Checkout UI\n(React)" as SC
  database "Local Queue\n(localStorage)" as LQ
}

package "Store Backend" #eff6ff {
  component "FastAPI Server" as API
  database "SQLite\n(WAL mode)" as SQLite
  component "Email Service\n(SMTP)" as Email
}

package "Dashboard" #fefce8 {
  component "Admin Dashboard\n(React)" as Dash
}

cloud "Couchbase Cloud" #fff1f2 {
  database "ica-checkout\nbucket" as CB
}

Customer --> SC : Shop & Pay
SC --> API : POST /transactions\n(online)
SC --> LQ : Cache tx\n(offline)
SC --> API : POST /heartbeat\n(every 5s)
SC --> API : POST /sync/offline\n(batch recovery)
API --> SQLite : Idempotent writes\n(UNIQUE constraint)
API --> CB : Sync transactions\n& heartbeats
API --> Email : Invoice emails\n(async)
Owner --> Dash : Monitor & Configure
Dash --> API : Dashboard APIs\n(poll every 5s)

note right of LQ
  **Offline-First Flow**
  1. Heartbeat fails -> offline mode
  2. Transactions saved to localStorage
  3. Background sync every 4s when online
  4. Idempotency keys prevent duplicates
end note

note right of CB
  **Cloud Sync**
  Best-effort replication
  of all transactions and
  terminal heartbeats
end note

@enduml
